trans-unit.source: Defines a method for adding the <xref uid="langword_csharp_DocumentStructure" name="DocumentStructure" href=""></xref> part of [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] to an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] package.

For more information about the `DocumentStructure` element of an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] package, see chapter 9 in the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] specification, which you can obtain at [XPS: Specification and License Downloads](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).

Adds the<xref uid="langword_csharp_DocumentStructure" name="DocumentStructure" href=""></xref> part of [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] to an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] package.

For more information about the `DocumentStructure` element of an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] package, see chapter 9 of the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] specification, which you can obtain at [XPS: Specification and License Downloads](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).

An <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsStructure"></xref> that represents the <xref uid="langword_csharp_DocumentStructure" name="DocumentStructure" href=""></xref> part of an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] package.
